      "span_text": "Subsequently this solution was incubated for 8 min at 100°C and was promoted with the thermal shock for 5 min at 2°C. The ureide-N concentration was determined at 535 nm in agreement with the colorimetric method described by  , in which alantoine was used as standard (Sigma chemicals)."
